UnityInventory - Inventory Management for Unity Missile System

Companion script to UnityPad that handles all inventory management:
- Item routing to designated containers
- Refinery and assembler feeding
- Tool/ammo/bottle production
- Miner connector transfers

Tag blocks with [PAD#] to match your pad.
Tag containers with [PAD#-ore], [PAD#-ingot], [PAD#-comp], [PAD#-tools], [PAD#-ammo], [PAD#-bottle]

Commands: SORT, RESCAN
